{
  "stem": "1216.3",
  "chunk_idx": 3,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 3.0,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "We had by then adapted to that kind of life.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I can't call it anything else.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And it was just an every day thing that needed to be done, and so we did it, and so we made a game of it.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "It's that simple.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "We decided what to catch, and then at a certain moment, we would catch for, let's say, five or 10 minutes, and then we would count the deads-- the dead ones.",
      "word_count": 31
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And whoever had more had won, and that was that.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Typical camp game.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Another camp game was we would go up to the attics.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "The barracks were meant for soldiers, of course, so the attics really didn't have rooms, except in the four corners.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And often they had been used for storage, and now they were also used for people.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "In between rooms, there was nothing.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "There were open beams, and you could kind of look through on whatever it was they used for ceilings below.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And in those open spaces lived rats.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "I don't know how they lived, they had no more to eat than we did, but they lived.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And one of our games was to poke them with a stick and make them jump, preferably over the beam.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And we thought that was very funny at the time.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "They never-- they did jump.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "They never attacked us, for whatever reason, either because they didn't have strength, or who knows why, but they didn't.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "And in those attics, presumably for moving things up and down, they had arches.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "And they would have probably hauled things up on a pulley and moved them in.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "There were no doors in those arches.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "Probably none were needed originally.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "And Hans and I would stand in there.",
      "word_count": 8
    }
  ],
